item.description:
Conforme solicitação do Silvano por e-mail (com a SDM Cíntia em cópia), a query foi alterada.
Antiga: select count(*) from gv$session where type not in ('BACKGROUND','FOREGROUND') and last_call_et/60 > 720 and status = 'ACTIVE' and event not like '%Backup%'
Nova query: SELECT count(*) FROM gv$session WHERE type NOT IN ('BACKGROUND','FOREGROUND') AND last_call_et/60 > 720 AND status = 'ACTIVE' AND event NOT LIKE '%Backup%' AND username NOT IN ('SYS','SYSTEM');
